417
00:44:19,700 --> 00:44:23,600
I wish you blue birds in the spring

418
00:44:23,600 --> 00:44:26,600
We sat somewhere
to rest for a while.

419
00:44:27,800 --> 00:44:30,600
I wasn't stupid.
I knew I was gonna see Christmas...

420
00:44:30,600 --> 00:44:32,400
from the back alley
of a shoestore.

421
00:44:35,400 --> 00:44:39,200
But still, I was totally
caughtup in spirit of things.

422
00:44:39,200 --> 00:44:43,200
I wanted to get him something,
give him something special.

423
00:44:44,800 --> 00:44:46,800
But when I got back...

424
