he was gone.

425
00:44:51,400 --> 00:44:53,300
It was Christmas Day.

426
00:45:01,800 --> 00:45:04,400
I never saw my daddy again.

427
00:45:10,000 --> 00:45:12,600
I never saw him again.

428
00:45:12,600 --> 00:45:15,200
I never saw my daddy again.

