00:45:28,400 --> 00:45:31,200
I'll always be here.
I love you.

430
00:45:32,200 --> 00:45:34,400
I love you.

431
00:45:34,400 --> 00:45:36,300
I love you, Charlotte.

432
00:45:49,000 --> 00:45:51,400
